I used dual-wielding/hasted pets for most of my xping. I tended to opt for lower level mobs, like dars or boks over krups, however. The average duration on charm was longer, and they were much less threatening on a charm break. Krups were normally only really safe with a few different people in the group who could help stun it... or if you abuse pathing in certain rooms in OS so the ex-pet needs to take about 10 seconds to reach you. Pathing is bad enough in Seb where I'm sure anyone could find the right spots.<P>--------------------<P>Tehom<BR>Cestus Dei<BR>Veeshan
