<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
For any given level, the same level mob will provide the same amount of exp (as a percentage of the bar) from the time you ding into the level to the time you ding out.  At lower levels, the difference between full exp and 50% exp is much more obvious than at higher levels; the more precise you want to be, the more mobs you kill, but it doesn't require as many.  If you're careful, it just takes one.  Make sure both pet classes are the same level, and both pets the same level (when you're using two pets), and fight mobs that are always the same level (this is most easily determined by fighting a mob that cons even to both of you).<P>--------------------<P>Waelquin Geistfessler<BR>High Elf Phantasmist of E'ci
</FONT>
